Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the cactus we heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called a Golden Barrel Cactus,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and takes 50 years until its flowers bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,50 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've raised it myself\Nsince it was this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:17.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Zenzō Sunada (66)\NWealthy Person
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Before I noticed, it'd already grown this big
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,and started blooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:28.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then you've been raising it since\Nyou were Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s age? {dropped ojisan}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} came here with her father to see it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Did that actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you won't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were just a toddler back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where're these important flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're blooming up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by spines, the yellow blooms look like a crown of feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem kinda odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:08.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:14.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Vivid summer memories surpass their season to solve mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:18.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rare cacti and painful spines in a\Ngreenhouse with flawless security.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:19.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really do have lots of cacti though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But some of them are valuable, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't thieves try and get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've got a custom alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When night comes, I'm the only one that can turn it off with this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like some smartcard from a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But why's it in your breast pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel most at ease when I keep important things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.96,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yasuyuki Sunada (36)\NPro Golfer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.96,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Naoki Sunada (33)\NImport Car Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We heard from the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You changed your will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! There are guests here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Just answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't argue with me! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your words'll rot the cacti!{adapted. original: The cacti'll die!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Bro... Let's come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get a proper answer out of you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly... and when the Golden Barrel's finally in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro, you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Misa Yashiro (27)\NHousekeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How may I please you, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to use bisque flowerpots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put them away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like we've come at quite a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently he used to be known as "Demon Zenzō" and was quite a shrewd person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, how embarrassing. Though\NI yelled at her, Yashiro does her job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her cooking's superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Completely different from{from? or is this a diff between en_GB and en_US? -uso.} my useless sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go back to the mansion for a while, so please, look round at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked you, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, what you're looking for is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're not leaving us an inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with the cacti, I'm donating it to a botanical garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you'd give your money to your cacti instead of your own sons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! What sort of job's a pro golfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't give money to sons who're all grown up and are still nipping at their father's heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, we came all the way out here to see them and they're only some tiny little flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be thankful that we were allowed to see some extremely rare flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a hot-water radiator?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably maintaining the temperature in the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this is the heat contro—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how can I get you to change your will back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph! As long as you don't intend to inherit my work, I'll never change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to stop golfing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a third-rate golfer who'll always get beaten in the preliminaries anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you've gone and said it, that's just what I'm gonna do!{mb misparsed, ask M_L言わせておけば いい気になりやがって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I get it! I'll just do what I want too then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What're you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just came here to extort money out of him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been sneaking around too, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in front of the master's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You come back for the first time in ages, and the only thing you can talk about is {\i1}money{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong... I'm concerned about you, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard the import car dealership you\Nonly just set up's already out of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What sort of concern is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't bother sucking up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing he can even think about is cacti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go picking fights, Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down for now and let's try and persuade him again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, looking at all that made me hungry somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, it's like the phrase "dumplings over flowers" was made for you.{Would render as "dumplings over flowers", but dango can also mean round things -- and Conan remarks about this phrase again later when Sonoko suggests she's getting fat(round), so idk what to do}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring my dinner to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} seems different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He gives me a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm full!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My stomach's bursting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, you ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kept asking for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When food's tasty, a girl wants to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go and practice golf outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go and look at the cars in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me the recipe for your gravy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Who do you want to make eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Honestly, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am honored to have pleased you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like some after-dinner coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be going about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your master still in the greenhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He tends to his cacti every night from 8 to 9 PM, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but the master instructed me that\Nhe was not to be disturbed until 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you wait a while longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have an after-dinner nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonoko, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're worrying about that {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that his will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was cerebral contusion{brain injuryI've had one of those -uso.} {+from? -uso.} from being hit from behind by a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is 8 to 8:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the first on the scene was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... The brats I always see at crime scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me what happened when you found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After dinner, we were talking in the living room, and at about 8:30, the greenhouse's alarm bell rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we ran over along with the housekeeper, Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in front of the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was holding Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that Mr. Zenzō changed his will lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after that, Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ran into the greenhouse with us following behind her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, go hear the others' stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, when the alarm bell rang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I rushed in and Dad had collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you at the greenhouse when you went to practice golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's because Dad sent me this e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Received at 8:20...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on the victim's phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also sent at 8:20 to Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the vic was alive till then.{victim (higaisha) was shortened to gaisha}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you standing outside the greenhouse holding the will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From my Dad's breast pocket, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro, then you really did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I didn't do it! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This had been dropped beside the corpse, do you recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A golf ball marker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know how it got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill my Dad! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:13:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Receiving an e-mail from the victim, you headed to the greenhouse under the pretense of golf practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having been invited in by the victim, you began arguing about the will,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and enraged, picked up a nearby shovel and beat Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you'd get the inheritance, you stole his will and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you triggered the alarm system and the alarm rang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The card to turn off the alarm should've been in Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s breast pocket too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why wouldn't he take that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had, the alarm wouldn't have rung.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deactivation card {\i1}was{\i0} in the victim's breast pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having hit his dad, he'd obviously be panicking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A potted pillar cactus was knocked down next to Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we first looked around in here, it wasn't knocked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because either the killer or the victim knocked it over when struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then isn't it odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The earth that spilled out of the pot is all dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it really dry out that much in just an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also, cactus spines are stuck in Zenzō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chest area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough! I'm tired of having brats sticking their noses into {\i1}every single investigation{\i0}!{Brats shouldn't stick their noses into every single investigation!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They've withered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:40.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...must be that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to take me in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll hear what you have to say at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So stop complaining and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I didn't do it! Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the alarm's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that alarm, I figured everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an alibi trick using the alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incident took place before Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} entered the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:16:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, when Mr. Zenzō entered the greenhouse at around 8 PM,\Nthe killer secretly crept in... and committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, in order to frame Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for it, they left at the scene a golf ball marker that only Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, using one of the fingers from the victim's corpse, the killer tapped out an e-mail calling Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and to conclusively prove their own alibi, scheduled it to be sent at 8:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you check with the phone company, they should confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the killer used the card to turn off the alarm which was in the victim's breast pocket and left the greenhouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then stealthily returned to the mansion by the back door, which can't be seen from the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Straight after running over to the crime scene, the killer returned the card to the corpse's breast pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why when Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stole the will, he didn't notice the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of course, the killer had it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the alarm rang, the greenhouse was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did the alarm ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a key to their trick, a trap set by the killer using an unexpected property of the alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look on top of that radiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two bisque flowerpots have been placed on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The greenhouse's alarm system checks for the small amount of far infrared rays the human body gives off and rings the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the pottery of bisque flowerpots is heated, they too give off the same far infrared rays as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer used that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will that really ring the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just conducted an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} told me to put those flowerpots on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why the alarm rang just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The situation was the same as when Yasuyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} entered the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bell did its task, and rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's only one person who could've commited this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misa Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only you could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was an interesting tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's simply a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that I'm the killer, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the killer beat the victim to death, he happened to knock over a cactus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the killer had to move the cactus from the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to steal the card to turn off the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When doing so, cactus spines got stuck into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, whoever has those wounds is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you say you aren't the killer, then by all means, show me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you said, I'm the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-These're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cacti told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I arrived at the crime scene, the earth spilled from the cactus's pot had already begun to dry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the flowers that were blooming this afternoon had for some reason withered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I had a flash of insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it was connected to the temperature in the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another key to solving the trick was the flowerpots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flowerpots which you had been scolded about and should have been tidied away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,somehow remained at the crime scene after the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer could only be Misa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, you were the only one who'd\Nknow where you'd put the flowerpots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I despised Zenzō Sunada...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was working, his management led other companies to go bankrupt one after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,driving many managers to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them was my father, who'd raised me without any help...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sunada retired, and advertised for a housekeeper, {sign: Housekeeper Wanted}\NI decided that I'd get revenge with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And seeing those perfect examples of prodigal sons who only had eyes for their father's fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought, why not frame one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I heard you were coming so suddenly, I did have second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, the family who spent all their time apart were all assembled...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hear the rest at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't understand your hate for Mr. Zenzō.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lost your dear father because of him.
